textAnnotations.description:
WE AMERICANS CELEBRATE OUR
DECLARATION OF INDEPENDENCE'S
RATIFICATION ON JULY 4TH, 1776..
. ONE YEAR AND
SIX WEEKS AFTER
NORTH CAROLINIANS
SIGNED THE MECK DEC!
